                        "text": "Ready for the journey of a lifetime? \ud83e\udd29\nExplore the untamed beauty of Sumatra, where ancient traditions meet pristine beaches and surf waves on the Mentawai Islands, and the lush jungles of Gunung Leuser National Park are home to incredible orangutans. \ud83c\udfc4\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83c\udf34\ud83e\udda7\u2728\n\n\ud83d\udccd Mentawai tribe\n\ud83d\udccd Pototoga Island\n\ud83d\udccd Bukit Lawang\n\nWhat is your dream destination? \ud83e\udd70\n\nJoin us @lunaswayfare on our next adventures in Indonesia! \ud83c\uddee\ud83c\udde9\n\n\ud83c\udde9\ud83c\uddea Bereit f\u00fcr die Reise deines Lebens? \ud83e\udd29\nErkunde die ungez\u00e4hmte Sch\u00f6nheit Sumatras, wo uralte Traditionen auf unber\u00fchrte Str\u00e4nde und Surfwellen auf den Mentawai-Inseln treffen und der \u00fcppige Dschungel vom Gunung Leuser Nationalpark die Heimat unglaublicher Orang-Utans ist. \ud83c\udfc4\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83c\udf34\ud83e\udda7\u2728\n\n#sumatra #indonesia #travelinspiration #reiselust #weltreise"
                    }
